Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:07.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息...我早晨的孕吐终于不再犯了!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Good news... my morning sickness is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还有个更好的消息...我做了个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Even better news... I had a great dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.60,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我和碧昂斯的好梦呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}about me and Beyonc?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.84,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯 你们俩这婚还结着哪\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence, I see you two are still married.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:18.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀...他们都觉得我们长久不了呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah... and they said it wouldn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"他们"就是指你啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And by "they," I mean you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.22,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这么开心的时刻来点栗子酱烤面包啊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Care for some toast with gooseberry jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.00,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,向我靠拢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.85,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你吃了 我就得吃\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Because when you gag, I gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.07,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,懂的 团结一心抵制它\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I got it, rock-solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:31.82,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美味无穷啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's quite tasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.53,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看起来像痰吐在了烤面包上\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}although it does look like phlegm on toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:35.87,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦 快停下来 - 不 你先停\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Oh, you gotta stop. - No, you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.25,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 为什么你偏偏要说到痰? - 你得停下来\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Why did you say phlegm? - You gotta stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.42,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快走开! - 快拿走!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Get it outta here! - Put it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,让这些奇怪的英式早餐\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, we might need to take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.73,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,高抬贵手放过我们吧\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}on the weird British breakfast food,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.34,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在孩子出生之前...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}at least until the baby is born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,长大之前...以及搬走以后\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and grows up... and moves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我去别的屋吃\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll eat it in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.62,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜我也应该把这些血肠带走\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm guessing I should also take this blood sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:01.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 别恶心啦! - 呃呃呃!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Stop it! - Uhhgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:03.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.42,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你买的这些姜味儿棒棒糖\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}These ginger lollipops you got me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:12.22,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的晨吐有很大的帮助呀\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}are really helping with the morning sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,给你秀一秀...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And look what I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:18.73,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你的嘴是长在哪儿的?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Where do you think your mouth is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.07,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不及要去农贸市场了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't wait to go to the farmers' market
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去秀秀我炫酷拉风的新推车!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and show off my sweet, new ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:27.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这位妈妈要去大采购啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ooh, Mama means business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.62,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我喜欢新买的手推车的味道\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ohh, I love that new cart smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该出去走走...现在是紫色花椰菜上市的季节\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We should get moving... it's purple cauliflower season,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,所以市场里肯定是热闹翻天!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and it's gonna be a madhouse down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:37.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.63,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 不好了不好了!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, it's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 用马桶塞一下搞定 因为我们的是节水马桶\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, just use the plunger. It's a low-flow toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,至多就5下\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Five squares max.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不!那些鲸鱼 它们在海湾里交配\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No! The whales, they're mating in the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:49.27,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 请不要用这样的措辞\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ew, don't call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是是真正的座头鲸在圣莫尼卡湾交配啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, actual humpback whales are mating in Santa Monica Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:56.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 如果我们动作快点 划小皮艇能近距离观赏高清无码版\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, if we hurry, we can kayak out there and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.77,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也别太近 不然可能会被现场氛围带进去跟着一块来一发了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, not too close, or you become part of the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我们已经有计划了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Anyway, we already have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是本月第三个星期天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's the third Sunday of the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.73,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我在说啥咩呀\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不能去天主教堂的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm not allowed in a Catholic church,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.05,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是你们的计划\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if that's your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.05,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是"嗨翻天的星期天"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, it's Sunday Funday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:17.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去最爱的农贸市场\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We go to our favorite farmers' market,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在好莱坞的那个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}the one in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去你的 影视城! - 哦!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Suck it, Studio City! - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:24.17,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我去农贸市场的时候还是在泰国\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Last time I was at a farmers' market was in Thailand,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我还以走私瓜果被控告\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I was accused of smuggling melons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在这个农贸市场同样有好戏上演\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, there's drama at this farmers' market, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.16,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,厄夫 卖小松糕的家伙 是个犹太人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Irv, the muffin guy, is Jewish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,但他老婆不是\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}but his wife is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,只是最近我很想去做一些刺激的冒险\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's just I've been craving a bit of adventure lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.36,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 嗯 这个 额\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, okay, well, the, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,目前只有利兹的房间没有被我们播撒过爱的种子了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}only room we haven't done it in is Lizzy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们当然有\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yes, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我当时没睡着哦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I wasn't sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的意思是\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, what I mean is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.67,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近过的都有点了无生趣\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've just been feeling a bit restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.64,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想说 这是我待过最久的地方\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, this is the longest I've stayed in one place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我结束了在摩洛哥做志愿者\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}since I was a volunteer in Morocco,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.81,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,改造扒手猴的生活以后\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}reforming pickpocket monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 你的人生真是充满了冒险啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wow, you've lived an adventurous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:12.62,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法和猴子比 除非是玩"运动冷知识" (手机游戏)\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't compete with monkeys,unless it's sports trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他们玩那个可烂了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}They suck at sports trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 在这个偷瓜贼出现之前\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Hey, you and I have had some pretty legendary adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有过几次相当传奇的冒险啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}before old melon smuggler here showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上次的公路之旅怎么样?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}What about our last road trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是租了一辆野营车一路向前疾驰\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Did you rent a camper van and just hit the open road,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,让风来指引你们的方向吗？\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}going where the wind takes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧...我们租了个面包车\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Close... we rented a minivan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.67,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,开到了圣地亚哥\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and we drove down to San Diego
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.32,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,清扫我阿姨的公寓\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}to clean out my aunt's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.01,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.64,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她有好多只猫\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And she had a lot of cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.68,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 然后他们还挺有个性 - 啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- and they had  attitude.- Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.34,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 重点是\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, the point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想冒险\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if you're looking for adventure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.65,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就是你的幸运日\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}today is your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.55,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说呢? 因为今天是星期天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}How do I know? 'Cause it's Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是唯一和 "嗨翻天"在读音上押韵的一天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and that's the only day that rhymes with "Funday"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.16,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一也挺押韵的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Except for Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.01,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,玩文字游戏的权利归我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Just leave the naming of the days to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.36,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨翻天的星期天 走起吧小婊砸们!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Sunday Funday, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,没说你们\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Not you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.03,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 他们还没演奏完\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Don't worry, they're not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,就是休息个五分钟\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}They're just taking a five-minute chai break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总是会停在这儿问候一下"谷粒和玫瑰"小乐团\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We always stop and give Grains N' Roses some love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前还从没见过有人能随着轻音乐扭摆呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've never seen anybody grind to easy listening before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.54,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦...这儿可真有点壮观\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wow... kind of a scene down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,紫花椰菜把所有男孩儿都吸引到院子里来了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Purple cauliflower brings all the boys to the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊...还有整车的大人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah... and that bus of seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 等一下\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.55,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们甚至还没走到生菜那里呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We haven't even gotten into the lettuces yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.65,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这仅仅是一叶障目...是的 我要说的是...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}This is just the tip... yep, I'm gonna say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,后面还有泰山 哈哈\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}of the "iceberg," heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在你俩对花生酱笑没完的时候...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}While you two are giggling over nut butters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.59,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿了一份当地的报纸\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I picked up a local paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.06,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那种报纸只会有广告\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, that paper just has ads
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.43,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,刊登着医用大麻和色情按摩的信息\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}for medical marijuana and dirty massages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.94,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最喜欢的报纸\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's my favorite paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,来看看封面故事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And look at the cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"给找刺激人士的洛杉矶指南"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"The Thrill-seekers Guide to L.A."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.67,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我一直在找的!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}This is exactly what I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.66,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看看啊 不觉得听起来特带劲儿么?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, doesn't this sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.97,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"在死亡峡谷高空跳伞"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"Skydiving in Death Valley."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈 - 那么说是有原因的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Huh. - Called that for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.68,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"夜登好莱坞标志"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"Climb in the Hollywood Sign at Night."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.47,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这个嘛... - 要是你想被谋杀的话\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Well... - If you wanna get murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.42,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦! "在马里布(加州著名海滩)滑翔"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Ooh! "Wingsuiting in Malibu."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.26,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我是想说... - 那就是直接进骨灰盒\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- I mean... - That's a closed casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看! 这儿有一个酒吧\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, look! There's a pub close by
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你能在哪里喝酒和玩儿蛇\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}where you can have a drink and play with snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们快点 我们能赶上两点的喂蛇互动环节\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, if we hurry, we can catch the 2:00 feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那个其实听起来还挺有意思的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}That actually sounds kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.27,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 拜托 你甚至都不喜欢蛇\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, please, you don't even like snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:46.19,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 也许是因为我从来没有边喝酒边和它们玩儿过\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, maybe 'cause I never play with them while drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 卢克 我想说这可是"嗨翻天的星期天"啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Enough, Luke, I mean this is Sunday Funday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.84,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,排队尝橄榄油的人越来越多了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}The line for the olive oil tasting is getting longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.34,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他快要没有夏巴塔面包了!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He's gonna run out of ciabatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有过轻按蛇的后背\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Have you ever flipped a snake on its back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.61,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还轻挠他的肚子?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and tickled its belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.18,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,它们真的会笑\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}They actually laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计 快点\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Dude, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 我们走\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Babe, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.99,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 卢克! - 亲爱的!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Luke! - Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这就是我的生活现状啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, this is my life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我夹在两个女人之间\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm stuck between two women,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.94,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这不是像那些业余电影人拍的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and it's not the romp some amateur filmmakers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那种电影里想让你相信的那样\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}would have you believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你说的话和\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm gonna tell you the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.37,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我上周告诉我表弟的话一样\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I told my cousin Chuck last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你的问题在于你有俩老婆\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Your problem is you got two wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.85,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,马库斯 利兹不是我老婆\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Marcus, Lizzy is not my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.67,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那就发短信告诉她你不回家吃晚饭了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Text her you're not coming home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.09,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能那么做...不回家吃饭得5点之前就告诉她\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Can't do that... would've needed to call her before 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一个月前\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, a month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.22,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你只需要考虑怎么\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}you only had to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,让利兹开心就行了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}keeping Lizzy happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,现在呢 你有了普鲁登斯\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And now, you have Prudence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.76,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,一个我猜测能以拉拉做不到的方式\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}who I'm guessing makes you happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.87,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,让你爽歪歪的人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}in a way a lesbian friend can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,从技术上来讲 拉拉做得到...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Technically, lesbians can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.41,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,她们只是不想这样做\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}they just don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.25,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是普鲁登斯想尝试新事物\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm just saying Prudence wants to try new things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.09,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你或许需要跟上她的步伐\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}so you might wanna get on board with her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在她觉得你无聊之前\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}before she gets bored with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.62,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得她会觉得我无聊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You think she's gonna get bored with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.30,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我都觉得你无聊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm  bored with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.23,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么事情也不干!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We never do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.02,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,只有工作 工作 工作\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's just work, work, work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.84,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们就是在这里工作啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Because this is where we work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}My point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,时不时的 给人家点惊喜\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}one of these days, surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭请假的事真是任重道远啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Dinner goes a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}To sum it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.02,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,如果普鲁登斯不那么痴迷于寻找刺激\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if Prudence wasn't so obsessed with her thrill-seeking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.99,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鲁克就会度过一个经典的"嗨翻天的星期天"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke and I would've had a classic Sunday Funday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.14,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用一直吃商店卖的廉价小胡萝卜\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I wouldn't be stuck eating store-bought baby carrots
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.67,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,像个普通的小婊砸一样\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}like a common whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.33,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 一条育儿小贴士\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Hey, a little parenting tip:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果要哄小孩睡觉\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if you ever need to put that baby to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,就给他讲这个农贸市场的故事吧\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}tell this farmers' market story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.48,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我把小公主城堡从车上拿下来了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, I dropped off the princess castle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,放在后院 下次你照看乔吉\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}in the backyard for the next time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.63,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以用了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}you babysit Georgie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.94,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿风有点大\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And it's kinda windy out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有合适的工具 所以...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I didn't have the proper tools, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.81,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡整个塌了也不用太惊讶\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}wouldn't be surprised if the whole thing fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 老姐 你们为啥把城堡玩具放在这？\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wait, Sissy, why are you guys leaving a play castle here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.33,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们自己家都没有\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You don't even have one for her at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们希望她在你家玩的开心\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We want your house to be fun for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是今年夏天我们去火人节的时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Especially this summer when we go to Burning Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.78,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 顺便告诉你 这个夏天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, by the way, you're watching her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.46,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去火人节的时候你得照顾她\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}this summer when we go to Burning Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.03,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我没错过农贸市场故事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I hope I didn't miss the rest of that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.60,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,的剩下部分\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}great farmers' market story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她还没说完 - 见鬼\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- She's still going. - Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And the other thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.37,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是他把农贸市场介绍给我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}he introduced me to this farmers' market.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直住在影视城这片市区的哎!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was all Studio City, all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,放松 老妹儿 你不会失去鲁克的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Relax, Sissy. You're not losing Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我确信这只是他一时没想清楚\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm sure his judgment's all clouded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.53,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,英国人在床上做一些很前卫的事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}British people do some funky things in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是听说过\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.32,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁克不会变成另一个人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke's not gonna turn into a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.99,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你是对的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I know, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.26,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,天了噜 你是谁?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像基版超级英雄\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Kinda looks like a gay superhero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.94,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,真理 正义 还有美国式的"嘿!"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Truth, justice, and the American "Heeey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你不是从飞机上跳下来的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Please tell me you're not jumping out of an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机多危险\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Planes are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我要从悬崖上跳下来\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm jumping off a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.90,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做普鲁登斯那个清单上\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm doing that wingsuiting thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.91,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,的滑翔挑战\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}from Prudence's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,有降落伞吗?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Is there a parachute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.15,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我估摸着有吧 - 你怎么着陆?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- I think so. - How do you land?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那准没好下场\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, that's not gonna end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我目睹过你看个奥运会\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've seen you sprain your ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,都能崴脚的经历\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}watching the Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松 我还得等好几个礼拜\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Relax, I don't actually soar off a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,才会从悬崖上跳下去呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}for a couple weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真是太危险了 他们都让你先\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's so dangerous they make you practice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.23,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个墙壁有软垫的风洞里练习\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}in a wind tunnel with padded walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有照过镜子啊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Have you looked at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.94,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你这德性可以跳过前面直接到有软垫的墙壁就行了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}'Cause you could skip right to the padded walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.78,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们走吧...乔治在车里等着呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Let's go... Georgie's waiting in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还开着空调\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}with the air conditioning on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.87,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松 美帝人民\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Relax, America.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们 你绝对会死翘翘的哟\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Dude, you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.25,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐 我都不敢相信\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God, I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会考虑要做这个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}you're even considering doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是 你就要做爸爸了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}especially since you're about to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.46,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过我也是普鲁登斯的丈夫呀\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, but I'm also a husband to Prudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.09,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我结婚誓词上说过的 "直到死亡将我们分开"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I made a vow: "Till death do us part."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不是今天就要死啊!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}That doesn't mean today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 如果普鲁登斯从桥上跳下去 你也跳?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, if Prudence jumped off a bridge, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们下周正要做这个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We're actually doing that next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.77,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你到底有啥毛病啊?! - 我没毛病啊!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- What's wrong with you?! - Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我...就是想稍稍改变一下现状\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I... just wanna change things up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.14,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一辈子都在保龄球馆上班\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I've worked at a bowling alley my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,做过最有异国范儿的事就是\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}The most exotic thing I've ever done
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在夫勒斯诺的时候和一个1/2亚洲血统的妹子啪啪啪\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}was sleep with a half-Asian girl in Fresno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.78,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你和张明 罗宾逊啪啪啪了?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You slept with Chang Ming Robinson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.85,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是重点 不过 是的 两次呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Not important, but, yes, twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.96,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 鲁克 开阔视野\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Listen, Luke, there are other ways
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:23.82,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他办法的 不是吗?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}to expand your horizons, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.82,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你的图书馆借书卡就在抽屉里呀\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Your library card is just sitting in your drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.09,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你个消息哦...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I got news for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.96,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,去图书馆 不在清单上\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}going to the library, not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,市中心那个都不在吗?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Not even the one downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.56,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,要进那个图书馆得经过金属探测器安检呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You have to go through a metal detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.98,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 你已经娶了普鲁登斯了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, you already got Prudence to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.23,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在试图证明什么呢?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}What are you trying to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我在试图留住她\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm trying to keep her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.61,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 啥? - 呃...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- What? - Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想让她觉得我无聊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just don't want her to get bored with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.65,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得你无聊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Bored with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.78,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你也看到她过得是什么样的日子了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah. You've seen the life she's lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,她啥都做过了 哪都去过了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}She's done everything, and she's been everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她什么时候会真的觉得你无聊么?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You know when she's really gonna get bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,当你挂了的时候!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}When you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 别那么大惊小怪的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, don't be so dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.82,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要去做?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Are you seriously gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.85,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是的! 今天我参加培训\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah! Today I train,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 我漫步云端\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}tomorrow, I taste the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候展翅高飞了 亲爱的!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's time to fly, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.26,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁克! 利兹!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke! Lizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.43,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.97,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我的亲娘四舅老爷啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么的这话对你这身打扮都是夸赞了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And somehow that's flattering on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.65,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他会好起来吗?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Is he gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.68,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 他有些轻微脑震荡\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, he has a slight concussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.14,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀脱臼\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}he dislocated his shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.04,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不得不打麻药才给他把肩膀弄回去\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and we had to put him under to reset it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,其实...也不是不得不\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well... we didn't have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.83,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这么大个汉子哭起来真是不忍直视\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}but it's hard to watch a grown man cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.06,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我还需要知道他的一些信息\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm gonna need some more information from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.40,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦! 好的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh! Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.06,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他的保险卡\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Here is his insurance card,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:41.00,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他之前医生的电话\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and a number to his primary doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他还是个小可爱时候的萌照\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and an adorable picture of him as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.85,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你好呀 小可爱\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他妻子咯?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, you're the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是哈\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, no, I'm his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的"拉"蜜啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, I'm his lesbian best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.32,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还怀着他的宝宝\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}She's having his baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住一起的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We all live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.17,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在算明白他为什么想自杀了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Now I can see why he tried to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,生日是什么时候呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Okay, uh, date of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我觉得他应该是冬天出生的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Um... I believe he was a winter baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是六月十九号好吗\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's June 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,在澳大利亚这就是冬天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}That's winter in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.02,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他对什么东西过敏吗?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Does he have any allergies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他喝了龙舌兰就会变得毛手毛脚的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He gets a little "handsy" on tequila.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.43,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他不能用青霉素 不能吃蘑菇\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He can't have penicillin, and he can't eat mushrooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.78,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只是他自己声称过敏啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}which he says is an allergy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.43,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只是不喜欢而已\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}but he just doesn't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.20,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你造吗 其实我只是假装在写\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You know what, I'm just gonna move my pen around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.96,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好让你们以为我把最后一句记下来了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}make you think I wrote that last part down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.64,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 普鲁登斯 这里交给我吧\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, Prudence, I've got this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想回家去\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if you wanna go home and change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.22,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的热气球装换下来\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}out of your hot air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.48,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用 我觉得\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, that's all right, I think Luke would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁克醒来的时候一定很想见到我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}want to see his wife when he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.07,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看 他在表示赞同哎\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}See? He agrees with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 他在痛的时候才会发出这种声音\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, that's the noise he makes when he's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他感觉不舒服了 得把他摇起来坐\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He's uncomfortable. He needs to be propped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是每晚和他睡一起的人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, I sleep with him every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.82,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜欢平躺着睡\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and he prefers to be flat on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.05,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是因为你是谁在他上面呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maybe if you're on top of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.55,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他会侧卧睡来清干喉咙\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But I know that he's prone to dry throat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.76,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为春假时他做急性腺体切除手术时我是在场的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}because I was there for his emergency adenoid surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.63,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我还费了老大劲才找到一个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}during spring break, and try finding a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.17,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,除了隆胸就什么都不会的医生\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}who does anything but breast implants in Tampa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.79,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能是比我认识他久一点\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, you may have known him longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.37,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,但是根据在内华达州的时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}but according to the state of Nevada
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那个给我们证婚的前妓女\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and the former prostitute who married us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.72,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是她的合法妻子\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm legally his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 一个都不知道丈夫生日的妻子!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, a wife who doesn't know her husband's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.27,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道他最喜欢的一集"星球大战"是\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, I know his favorite "Star Wars"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"帝国反击战"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}is "Empire Strikes Back."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧 所有人都最喜欢这集\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, that's everybody's favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 把遥控器给我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 给我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, you give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 有些时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, you've got to hand over the reins
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你该要把选择权交给卢克\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}to Luke at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.42,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾他如今是我的职责了好吗!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's my job to look after him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.62,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,噢真的吗 你可照顾得真好啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, really? Well, great job looking after him, Prudence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是因为你\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}because, if it wasn't for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不会神志不清地躺在医院里\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}he wouldn't be lying unconscious in a hospital bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.10,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了取悦你\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}trying to impress you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.60,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是事实\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.00,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他以前从来没穿过滑翔服\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He doesn't wingsuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.90,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有跳过伞或者潜过水\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and he's never skydived or dove or "doven"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不像你过去那样搞空中飞人的把戏\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}or however you skydive in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是想向你证明他是爱冒险的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}He was just trying to prove to you that he's adventurous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,他确实是呀\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But he is adventurous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.61,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 在床上 我们...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, sexually, we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.47,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,偏题了好吗!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}That's not what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 他就是在拼命迎合你的喜好\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look, he just was going along with what you wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他害怕你会觉得他无聊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}because he was scared that you were gonna get bored with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.35,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,搭把手啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.84,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的时候总是没人看见\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Of course, when no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在都能独自去浴室了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}So, I just completed my first solo trip
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜我们大家\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}to the bathroom, so I guess we're all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,都对此深感欣慰\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}pretty happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.50,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你都好差不多了 我想我可以说了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Now that you're okay, I think I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.34,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都从这次经历中收获了点啥\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}we both got something out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你开始学飞 而我是对的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You got to fly, and I got to be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:27.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说 和飞一样爽\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}which, for me, is like flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:32.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克 我给你做了我妈出了名的秘制蔬菜汤\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Luke, I made you my mum's famous vegetable soup recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,其实就是水和胡萝卜\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's just water and a carrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没种出别的来\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}We didn't have much growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.93,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这里面可是满满的爱呦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But there's plenty of love in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然主要的原料还是水\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But the main ingredient is water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.04,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.31,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是普鲁登斯啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm Prudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.18,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你老婆\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.42,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,一个关于脑震荡后的小幽默啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}A little post-concussion humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该看看 利兹提到宝宝\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You should've been there when Lizzy mentioned the baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.25,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我说 "我们做过了?" 以后她的表情\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and I said, "We went through with that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.00,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过还是他幽你一默的时候更搞笑\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, but it's so much funnier when he does it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我在想我的肋骨一长好...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Anyway, I was thinking, once my ribs fuse back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.33,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能继续去完成你清单上的项目了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}we can start checking stuff off your list again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.02,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 我们可以试一个别的清单\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Or we could try another list.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.19,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"全城十大最适宜静坐的地方"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"Ten Best Places to Sit Quietly Around the City."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.55,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看来 市中心有一片干草坪\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Apparently, there's a dry patch of grass downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是必去的胜地啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}that's a must-try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛读《美国退休者协会杂志》?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Why are you reading "AARP" magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.83,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那是我的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Hey, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这期的封面故事可是莉莉 汤普琳(美国演员)\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}There was a Lily Tomlin cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.39,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我没明白 "一片干草坪?"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'm sorry, "a dry patch of grass?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这到底怎么回事儿? - 没事儿啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- What's going on? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是我已经有过了很多次的冒险经历\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's just that I've had plenty of adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是时候静下心来了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Maybe it's time to calm things down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:52.02,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,学学做数独啦...或者看看"海军罪案调查处"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Learn Sudoku... or watch "NCIS."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.46,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这不是你风格啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But that's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.81,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 事实证明滑翔也不是你的风格\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, it turns out wingsuiting isn't really you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.68,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想说什么啊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.65,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我意思是 没错 我是出了点小事故\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I mean, sure, I had a little accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.28,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在呼吸 说话和嘘嘘的时候会有点疼\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and it hurts when I breathe, talk, and pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不代表我不会再尝试新鲜事物啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}but it doesn't mean I wanna stop trying new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.46,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那你为什么要担心我会觉得你无聊啊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, then why are you worried that I'm gonna get bored with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说我担心你会觉得我无聊啊?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Who said I was worried about you getting bored with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉她了?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You told her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你告诉她了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Because you told her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是 你为什么不告诉我\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And the question is, why couldn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样 普鲁登斯 等一下 听我解释啊!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, Prudence, wait. Let me explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.18,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你都干什么好事了?!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.54,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Prudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.51,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是难以置信你居然告诉了普鲁登斯\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't believe you told Prudence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.24,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心她会觉得我无聊的事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was scared she was gonna get bored with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.04,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是还给她看了那张有个夏天\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Did you also show her pictures of me from the summer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.99,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我又胖又满身是糖霜的照片?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was fat and had frosted tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.05,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,没有! 还没聊到那么久远呢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No! There's no coming back from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.58,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想我怎么做?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}What did you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时正跳进一个那么危险的火坑\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You were jumping through very dangerous hoops,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,还想成为那种你原本不是的人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}trying to be someone you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹 我没成为另一个人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy, I'm not a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.19,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想试着突破一下我们的生活方式\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I was just trying to break the mold a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.73,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我喜欢我们的方式\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But I like our mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.63,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,它一直伴随着我们\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's shaped like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.99,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但现在我们要习惯普鲁登斯在我们之间插一脚\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, now we have to fit Prudence inside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.29,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,或者换个方式表达这个意思\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Or a different way of saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:15.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我懂了 不再仅仅只有我们两个人了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}But I get it, it's not just the two of us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.19,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉好糟糕啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我不应该和她说 你的事故是她的错\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I shouldn't have told her your accident was her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.74,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该和她说 我和你说过的话的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I should've just told her what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到她的时候 应该把这些都告诉她\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And when we find her, we should tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.81,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经告诉我了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.76,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.92,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了...你是英国人\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I get it... you're British,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,所以当你不开心的时候 你就去找离你最近的城堡\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}so when you're upset, you find the nearest castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.09,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们不高兴的时候就会喝两杯 一醉解千愁\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, when we're upset, we drink and don't let it show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.83,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不过借酒浇愁愁更愁\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Until we really let it show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.00,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 我不是故意让你不高兴的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Baby, I didn't mean to get you upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.14,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想让你觉得我很了不起\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just wanted you to think I'm awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.90,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我猜我只是习惯了和利兹\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I guess I'm just used to talking to Lizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.07,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,无话不说\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,无话不说?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.87,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是我们昨晚做那件事情时候用了...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Even that thing we did last night with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不包括那个 - 他没和我说那个\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Not that. - He did not tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.15,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是忍不住去想 如果我像她一样了解你\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I just can't help feeling that none of this would've happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.15,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,那所有这些都不会发生\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}if I knew you like she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.97,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,她遥遥领先你30年\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}She's had a 30-year head start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.12,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为什么有时候对我来说\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Which is why it's a little tough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,和别人共享他会有点困难\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}to share him sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.52,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Most times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.81,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,任何时候!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}All the times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.91,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道 我永远都不会让你因为我受伤\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You have to know I'd never want you to get hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 除了你这么要求的时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Well, unless you were asking for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.04,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,比如耳光式的卧室情趣 之类的情况\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}like a slappy bedroom kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.17,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你们是在那儿鼓掌\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I thought you guys were clapping in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.08,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个声音烦死我了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}and  that  bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.18,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的 昨天晚上确实是在鼓掌\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, last night was actual clapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.55,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我大展了雄风\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I did a really good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:44.49,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的很爱你...所以你可以什么都和我说\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I really do love you... and you can tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.91,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道...我爱你\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I know... and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.75,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"我爱你哦"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.32,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,"我也爱你呢"\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}"I love you, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.19,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我想身边有个找刺激的人也挺不错\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}And I guess it's kinda good to have
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.90,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我俩肯定不会做这种事\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}a thrill-seeker around, 'cause it's certainly not us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.64,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你的冒险大胆程度可远超你对你自己的评价\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You're bigger risk-takers than you're giving yourselves credit for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.84,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在说我的羊毛衫?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Are you talking about my cardigan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.23,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不太确定穿它是不是需要很大胆\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}'Cause I wasn't sure about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.37,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我在说事实\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}No, I'm talking about the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.18,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要一起有个孩子了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}you're having a baby together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.69,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这很勇敢\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's quite brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们正在创造属于你们自己定义的家庭\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You're creating your own definition of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.73,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.21,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说你觉得穿这件羊毛衫是疯了\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}So you think the cardigan's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确不是特别喜欢啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}It's not my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.13,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴吧\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.80,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦...爬上好莱坞的标志\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wow... climbing up to the Hollywood Sign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.48,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,可真是一个好主意 利兹\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}was a really good idea, Lizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.16,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是不敢相信 我竟然完成了恐怖清单上的一项\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't believe I did something off the scary list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.14,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,做个坏人感觉真好\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Feels good to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,知道还有什么会让你感觉很好么?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Know what else feels good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.44,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,带着你伤痕累累的肋骨徒步爬上这儿来\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Doing that hike up here with bruised ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.79,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能等个两三天么?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Couldn't have waited two, three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.70,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 可怜的亲亲\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Oh, poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你振作起来的\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I'll help you get back on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.86,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说"骑在我背上吧"?\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Don't you mean "back on my back"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.93,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,- 喔 - 嗯...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}- Oh... - Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.57,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这样让我支持你俩在一起真是好难\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You make it so hard to root for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.37,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道么 如果你离得非常非常近\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}You know, if you look really, really close,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.71,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,你就可以分辨出\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}you can just make out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.87,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,农贸市场的那些帐篷啦\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}the tents of the farmers' market.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.88,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,利兹...\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Lizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.91,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是不敢相信 30年来我们居然没这么做过\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}I can't believe in 30 years we've never done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.45,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们...这是我们第一次\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Look at us... this is our first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.95,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,一起进行真正的冒险\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}real adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.11,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 是这样\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是当这种冒险还是违法的时候\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Especially since it's illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.89,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.68,大家庭,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你说啥?!\N{\fs14\fnHelvetica\fe0}Wait, what?!

